Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.46,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}理由があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.71,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}偶然でも　成り行きでも
