Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.21,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.46,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
